  ('dietitian-moex-01473', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-109-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關消化道的三種脂解酶特性，下列何者正確？', '["不論linguallipase、gastriclipase或pancreaticlipase之作用皆需膽鹽參與", "linguallipase、gastriclipase或pancreaticlipase皆適於中性作用", "乳脂肪的短（或中）鏈脂肪酸常位於三酸甘油酯的sn-2位置", "linguallipase與gastriclipase偏好水解含短（或中）鏈脂肪酸之三酸甘油酯"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5d78b7232cbb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "619f53d61f1c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109030", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01474', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-109-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關棕色脂肪與白色脂肪不同點的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["棕色脂肪負責能量儲存及提取，白色脂肪負責產熱", "兩者的產熱能力均來自細胞膜的去耦合蛋白-1（UCP-1）", "只有棕色脂肪的脂解作用（lipolysis）涉及交感神經活化PKA的途徑", "成人有較多棕色脂肪者，有助於對抗肥胖並提高胰島素敏感性"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5d78b7232cbb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "619f53d61f1c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109030", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-01475', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-109-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關飲食組成對膽固醇含量之影響，下列何者正確？', '["所有飽和脂肪酸均會提高血膽固醇量", "攝取過多的醣類會提高血膽固醇量", "動物性油脂中的硬脂酸（stearicacid）影響最為顯著", "月桂酸（lauricacid）、肉荳蔻酸（myristicacid）、棕櫚酸（palmiticacid）影響最為顯著"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5d78b7232cbb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "619f53d61f1c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109030", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
